    <abstract>
      <t>   This document describes a flexible method for selecting candidate
   Segment Routing (SR) policy paths. Based on the real-time resource
   usage and forwarding quality of candidate paths, the head node can
   perform dynamic path switching between multiple candidate paths in
   the SR policy.

	 </t>
